                Akyuzakyuzmuhammed@gmail.com<br>
                akyolakyolmuhammet@gmail.com
            </p>

            <h4 class="h06">Address</h4>
            <p>
                4500 Sokak Yazılımcılar Mah.<br>
               İzmir/Karabağlar<br>
                35000 TR
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>